# Cybersecurity : CSN150
Project: ESP32 Access Point
## Purpose
Create an ESP32 Wifi Access Point (AP) for web server projects. 
This way, you don’t need to be connected to a router to access the web server. 
We’ll program the ESP32-CAM using Arduino IDE.

